  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IncompatiblePredicateArityException
    Expression thrown when attempting to load facts for a Predicate from a DataSource that does not contain data of the specified arity.
    PrefixDeclarationException  
    ReasonerStateException
    Thrown when an operation that is invalid in current reasoner state is attempted.
    RulewerkException
    Top-level checked exception for Rulewerk system.
    RulewerkRuntimeException
    Superclass of unchecked exceptions generated by Rulewerk.
